	pages = {3608--3614},
	annote = {- criticizing other studies for using binned precipitation and temperature to figure out relationship between temperature and precipitation changes, proposes instead a method using quantile regression- using quantile regression to get change in high end of preciptiation results in more efficient estimators than using equal distance bins of precipitation / temperature both in terms of sample sizes and number of covariates. Additionally, quantile regression is unbiased withs ample size and has lower result variance.},
